<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Application Update - Lona</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f7f9fb;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">

  <!-- Email Container -->
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f7f9fb;padding:48px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">

        <!-- Header -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 32px;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:32px 16px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0;font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#0040e0;">Lona</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- Main Content Card -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(25,28,30,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(196,197,217,0.15);margin:0 0 48px;">

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 32px;">

              <!-- Header Section -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 32px;">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.2;">
                      Application Review Notice
                    </h2>
                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#434656;">
                      Regarding: <strong><%= projectTitle %></strong>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Introduction Text -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 32px;">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      Hello <strong><%= userName %></strong>,
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      Thank you for taking the time to submit your application and complete the interview questions for the <strong><%= projectTitle %></strong> opportunity.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      As part of our standard review process to ensure authenticity and fairness for all candidates, all interview submissions undergo automated and manual analysis.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- AI Detection Flag Block -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;background-color:#ffdad6;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 32px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px;">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="width:60px;vertical-align:top;padding-right:20px;">
                          <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);border-radius:50%;text-align:center;line-height:48px;">
                            <span style="color:#ba1a1a;font-size:24px;">🛡</span>
                          </div>
                        </td>
                        <td style="vertical-align:top;">
                          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#93000a;">
                            Automated Content Flag
                          </h3>
                          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#93000a;line-height:1.5;">
                            Our analysis systems indicate that your interview responses strongly exhibit patterns consistent with AI-generated text.
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Explanation and Decision -->
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 40px;">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      At Lona, we require all applicant responses to reflect original thought and direct personal experience. Because the content flagged in your submission violates our guidelines for authenticity, we are unable to process your application for this specific project.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 32px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      We take these matters seriously to maintain the integrity of our matching process for both professionals and clients. This decision is final for the <strong><%= projectTitle %></strong> role.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#191c1e;line-height:1.6;">
                      Regards,<br/>
                      <span style="font-weight:500;color:#191c1e;">The Lona Review Team</span>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="text-align:center;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 16px 40px;">

              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 16px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:0 16px;">
                    <a href="#" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;">Privacy Policy</a>
                  </td>
                  <td style="color:#cbd5e1;font-size:12px;">•</td>
                  <td style="padding:0 16px;">
                    <a href="#" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;">Terms of Service</a>
                  </td>
                  <td style="color:#cbd5e1;font-size:12px;">•</td>
                  <td style="padding:0 16px;">
                    <a href="#" style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:underline;">Unsubscribe</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;">
                © <%= year %> Lona. All rights reserved.
              </p>

            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
